snippet.title: NEW Amber Heard Busted Admitting Punching JD.
snippet.description:
This is another recording of Johnny Depp trying to reason with Amber Heard and get her to accept her abuse. She in typical psycho mode twists things around, admitting to punching and hitting him repeatedly and saying that Johnny is to blame because he walks away and so this guarantees he gets beaten up by her.
Trial day 1 
https://youtu.be/IsT87oDIc6I
Trial day 2
https://youtu.be/FQZxYkteyQU
https://youtu.be/U1FURtwJOmk
Trial day 3
https://youtu.be/nxciqxT81PE
Trial day 4
https://youtu.be/XVO7Jv2w1kA
Week 1 Recap
https://youtu.be/Ivv7Qt1CqeA

Week 2
Trial day 5
https://youtu.be/NPDAQY2fGSg
Trial day 6
https://youtu.be/EUtBchKJd_4
https://youtu.be/eUxzeK7PVLE --- Johnny Depp testifies
Trial day 7 
https://youtu.be/RCV-dNClAww --- Johnny Depp testifies against Amber Heard
